					<div><input type="radio" name="vote1" />C、送分送礼物</div>
					<div><input type="radio" name="vote1" />D、赠送优惠券</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="voteDiv">
				<div class="voteTitle">4、网购时，你经常使用哪种付款方式？</div>
