					<div><input type="radio" name="vote4" />A、网上支付</div>
					<div><input type="radio" name="vote4" />B、货到付款</div>
					<div><input type="radio" name="vote4" />C、邮局汇款</div>
					<div><input type="radio" name="vote4" />D、银行转账</div>
